{
  "stem": "21817.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "On top of the building used to be machine guns.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they used to take us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Since we were all civilian, we didn't know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we used to carry the ammunition, those boxes, way on top, on the top roof.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because they were expecting some, some attack from partisan or whatever.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There were already groups of partisan or, or ex-soldiers that did, that did not surrender.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, and at that time, the situation changed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were more careful with, with shooting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because everybody knew what was happening that particular day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we went back to work at the station over there, digging in the sand, filling in those cars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And at lunchtime, they were already-- pardon me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I have to go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Mostly, those soldiers who were watching us were older Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were not the young fellows like that were going to the front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they're watching us and building that station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And during lunchtime, they, they give us a little freedom, the civilian, not the military.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we used to sneak out, go around, look what's going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We used to go over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Close by were also farmers, small farms, farmhouses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We used to go and beg for a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Sometimes they, they prepared some bread for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Sometimes they told, we don't have any more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then I find out that there is-- maybe a couple feet from me was a, a major street going to the airport.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Well, the camp was at one place where they kept us, because we were building the new station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And not too far was the airport, maybe a half a mile, a mile.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
